{"word":"χλιαίνω","slug":"χλιαίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>χλιαίνω</b></el> <el>(χλῑαίνω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:χλίω'><el>χλίω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to warm</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to heat</i> with passion:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be so heated</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}